{"tid":1559486,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2年前始測試人面辨識　智慧燈柱鬼祟分拆上馬","createTime":"2019-09-11T00:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T04:51:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc3e2b6622e9bd21bcb3d56a4f41137f7329c67","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190911/large/1568131492_74fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190911%2Flarge%2F1568131492_74fc.jpg&h=419c0458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍灣智慧燈柱倒下一幕，成為反送中運動其中一個標誌性畫面。政府多番否認「多功能智慧燈柱」具備人面辨識功能，惟《蘋果》調查發現，政府早於2017年測試燈柱及相關可辨識及追蹤行人的「智慧人流管理系統」，至近月才突然封口不提。<br />\n<br />\n創科局早前申請撥款時，更將這個高達2億元的燈柱項目「分拆」成多條小帳目，綑綁其他小型民生工程一併申請，以避過財委會獨立審批。議員認為做法令人感覺「鬼祟」，令市民更添懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n記者 梁御和"},{"pid":"3bdf887616bf60ca57f7ed6ac611e457cfda39ca","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:01:24.000Z","msg":"政府最早透過「起動九龍東」計劃，進行一系列涉及多功能燈柱的概念驗證（Proof of concept）測試，包括在2017年的「香港街馬」活動中，測試「智慧人流管理系統」。活動當日，跑道樽頸位和輪候地點均安裝閉路電視，以人流系統分析攝錄畫面；根據官方的介紹影片，系統可辨識畫面中所有行人及車輛，以綠色方框加以標示，再點算及追蹤目標。<br />\n<br />\n一年後，政府分別在九龍東安裝7支多功能燈柱作概念驗證測試，又宣佈展開為期3年的「多功能智慧燈柱試驗計劃」，陸續在九龍灣、觀塘、中環、金鐘、銅鑼灣、灣仔及尖沙咀更換400支智慧燈柱。翻查發展局及創科局的立法會文件，清楚列明燈柱具備統計人流及車流功能。<br />\n<br />\n至今年，新彊監控及信用系統問題漸被關注。政府資訊科技總監辦公室曾在4月一次公開活動展示智慧燈柱的模型，根據當日新聞片段，模型具備辨識及追蹤行人功能。不過，同月的立法會文件已再沒提及有關功能；資科辦最近亦多番澄清，指燈柱現時收集的數據「不涉市民私隱及個人資料」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568110103_6c2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568110103_6c2a.jpg&h=b0322bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智慧人流管理系統可辨識攝錄畫面中所有行人及車輛，以綠色方框加以標示，再點算及追蹤目標。官方介紹影片截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568110103_2695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568110103_2695.jpg&h=0cef76d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府在2017年開始透過「起動九龍東」計劃，為「多功能燈柱」及「智慧人流管理系統」進行概念驗證（Proof of concept）測試。官網截圖"},{"pid":"2a66c503ebc29c1104ff9d671dc5e5b7bf3ddba0","tid":1559486,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"毒果又擠牙膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d925f3ca833b85b5f24d8338bd556f7ec8ea36","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"監控燈柱關注組發言人陳先生指，人流管理系統與人面辨識系統在原理上相同，都是利用燈柱鏡頭進行攝錄，再經後台系統進行人工智能分析。「基本上中國信用系統所需要嘅硬件佢（智慧燈柱）都齊晒，後台有咩處理其實市民好難得知&hellip;&hellip;只要見到樣，AI就認到。」<br />\n<br />\n他又指，即使政府文件寫明燈柱的數據不會交予第三方，但處理數據的雲端平台可信性成疑，過往就有中國的雲端平台被踢爆以保安為名將數據複製取走。<br />\n<br />\n首批50支燈柱已安裝在觀塘及九龍灣一帶， 餘下350支會在未來3年內完成，整項工程涉款2.72億元。按慣常做法，創科局要向財委會申請一筆過撥款，並提交項目的獨立文件供議員質詢審批。<br />\n<br />\n不過，翻查財委會文件，智慧燈柱申請撥款的過程極為「隱秘」，被「拆件」成多項小型工程，亦即「啟德/九龍灣安裝工程（1008萬元）、銅鑼灣安裝工程（485萬元）及資訊科技系統（989萬元）等3條小賬目，分別夾附在基本工程儲備基金的「公路」及「電腦化計劃」分目內，綑綁其他不相關的小型民生工程作整體審批，今年2月獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n基本工程儲備基金的設立原意是加快小型工程的審批程序，撥款不超上限（大多定於3,000萬元以下）的工程可一併作整體審批，不用向財委會提交獨立文件，變相避開議員討論和質詢。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技界立法會議員莫乃光指，創科局去年曾向議員承諾會為智慧燈柱、數碼個人身份（eID）及新一代政府雲端基礎設施（政府雲）獨立申請一筆過撥款，「點知突然用咗其他方法（綑綁基金）去拎錢。」<br />\n<br />\n莫稱，有關做法令議員無法正常審議燈柱項目，事後也難作跟進。他不揣測政府動機，但認為此舉令市民更懷疑當局是要將項目「偷偷」推上馬。「市民對政府已經有信任危機，未來推展工作只會更加困難。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568109920_fb9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568109920_fb9d.jpg&h=240bac64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568109920_7ce0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568109920_7ce0.jpg&h=37f38ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被分拆後的啟德及九龍灣智慧燈柱安裝工程及銅鑼灣安裝工程，分別夾附在基本工程儲備基金的「公路」分目，由於工程費不高於3000萬元，毋須獨立審批，也不用向財委會提交獨立文件。財委會文件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568109920_655b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568109920_655b.jpg&h=272616e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智慧燈柱的資訊科技系統被分拆夾附在基本工程儲備基金的「電腦化計劃」分目，工程費不高於1000萬元，同樣毋須獨立審批。財委會文件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568109922_a829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568109922_a829.jpg&h=8f2c62e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智慧燈柱項目涉款2.72億元，政府卻將項目「分拆」成多條小帳目，夾附在基本工程儲備基金的「公路」及「電腦化計劃」分目內，與其他小型民生工程作綑綁式審議。財委會文件"},{"pid":"01d78fbf5cc35e86b3ecdd2cdde990faa0d4d0a9","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:03:34.000Z","msg":"資科辦回覆指，去年向立法會匯報試驗計劃時，已表明需就各推展地區的路面交通、設施情況諮詢區議會，建議要按實際情況分階段推行，最後採取有別於eID及政府雲的方式申請撥款，今年4月也曾在立法會文件上提及，不存在「偷偷」上馬。<br />\n<br />\n資科辦又指，4月時的確在博覽活動展示「入場人數計算技術」，不過早前已澄清智慧燈柱試驗計劃不會應用有關技術、也沒有人臉識別功能；當局現時亦設專責委員會檢視燈柱的私隱保障問題，目標今年底前提交報告。"},{"pid":"968d38fb35dcce65101a21bca6bbf3084fcbe724","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:03:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190911/60029575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60029575&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRenG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=5bb77ff0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190911%2F60029575&h=ead0376e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190911/60029575</a>"},{"pid":"f60802a8c5290f664831566eb215f65d027898c3","tid":1559486,"uid":273716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:04:27.000Z","msg":"港共成日話枝燈柱冇人面識別AI<br />\nclient side緊係冇架，係server到做呀嘛<br />\n真係當香港人白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee9f4a5f1705a805037568d3fe9fb17f0e45c9a","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f992a57fd8d15bbd9eb5b92ba7c498c52c1fa58c","tid":1559486,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:09:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d0bf4b0a48ee9bd493ef3860f65999e5a5be649f","tid":1559486,"uid":240522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:10:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f3c15f7332a6b18fe0d66d24704efad11edeabe","tid":1559486,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"612 721 831"},{"pid":"158b294ef30bcf110ff3e9564cf01b0312fc8f23","tid":1559486,"uid":24853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:14:29.000Z","msg":"呢個政府真係鬼到仆街 <br />\n你話唔推翻點得"},{"pid":"1652beaa0328b109ccb90603a5111461e5a53abe","tid":1559486,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e0cd91efdf0bf2672eaa2738936f1ff27d6093","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abc03d13ae48df31df3edc75931d7b02a033086","tid":1559486,"uid":82454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:19:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b182ce83aefdf8826cba40dd9dee0b151122aa09","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930d980d07ce64285afc7838d2854908bb7cf7fe","tid":1559486,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fea9fd53e86e056e9692cbd2a193e65f96e1f1b","tid":1559486,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abe0f2f4a167864fe37cbd6011a59a67c9870abe","tid":1559486,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"on9 正苦當人傻架咩<br />\n<br />\n係垃圾C9 藍絲先會俾你垃圾正苦呃到"},{"pid":"ae79e6a172afae04c77ea943828c8fee9fe40d1e","tid":1559486,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8768f701e2a483083a4bc76fc41ea0f47cfe15f6","tid":1559486,"uid":12334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:24:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87737d24abe4c4d2fd630f772e08bc995dad2875","tid":1559486,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"913 各大公園<br />\n<br />\n914 天水圍/中學生/獅子山？<br />\n<br />\n915 民陣遊行"},{"pid":"078480f02e95ecce15b0345a1f4390f499e96170","tid":1559486,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"監控燈柱，屌那星"},{"pid":"80d4bc3dafc5f657bfcf29a8010b24999